{"tid":2486040,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"我部電話癡撚咗線","createTime":"2021-04-12T14:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T15:43:50.000Z","uid":75218,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc80883fc9060d35480b528304a91e72b86ebf0a","tid":2486040,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"大家可以起我底睇番，大概10幾日之前（2021年3月中）我一個用咗10幾年嘅WhatsApp電話俾人哋封鎖咗.<br />\n<br />\n-我從來都冇用個Account進行商業活動<br />\n-亦都冇講過任何關於兒童色情嘅嘢<br />\n-亦都冇使用第三方嘅應用程式去開啟WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n咁總之啦我都幾肯定我係冇違反WhatsApp講嘅Terms of Service <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦如是者咁我個WhatsApp比人哋封鎖咗啦，咁當然有出個email比WhatsApp支援，但從來都冇得到過任何回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可能你會問你俾人封鎖咗喺度講做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直至今日我見到福布斯有條新聞<br />\n，就係有一班hackers 可以bypass 任何 security ，去令到人地個whatsapp 帳號永久封鎖<br />\n<br />\nSource : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/zakdoffman/2020/03/29/new-whatsapp-attack-thieves-now-using-this-hack-to-steal-accounts-update-your-security-settings/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fzakdoffman%2F2020%2F03%2F29%2Fnew-whatsapp-attack-thieves-now-using-this-hack-to-steal-accounts-update-your-security-settings%2Famp%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=7575b1f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/zakdoffman/2020/03/29/new-whatsapp-attack-thieves-now-using-this-hack-to-steal-accounts-update-your-security-settings/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我就黎手 ，去百佳買咗幾張$33嘅電話卡，我發現只要我用部電話去開任何WhatsApp帳號，嗰個account都會立即俾人封鎖.<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想問： Samsung S21 ultra 好唔好用?<br />\n<br />\n用緊iPhone 12 pro"},{"pid